<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Scheduled Maintenance</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light dark;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1f2937 0%, #111827 35%, #0b1120 100%);
      color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      width: min(420px, 100%);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.72);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      color: #0b1120;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .status {
      margin: 1.75rem 0 0;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .status strong {
      color: #f9fafb;
    }

    .pulse {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #38bdf8;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.7);
      display: inline-block;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% {
        transform: scale(0.9);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
      }
      70% {
        transform: scale(1);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0);
      }
      100% {
        transform: scale(0.9);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(56, 189, 248, 0);
      }
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.75);
    }

    a {
      color: #38bdf8;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <article class="card" role="status" aria-live="polite">
    <span class="badge"><span class="pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span> Maintenance Mode</span>
    <h1>We&rsquo;re getting things ready</h1>
    <p>
      The assessment platform is briefly unavailable while we run maintenance tasks.
      Your data stays safe, and we&rsquo;ll bring the service back online as quickly as possible.
    </p>
    <div class="status">
      <strong>What&rsquo;s happening?</strong>
      <span>Our team is refreshing the infrastructure and verifying database connectivity.</span>
      <span>Most maintenance windows finish in just a few minutes.</span>
    </div>
    <footer>
      Need assistance? Contact <a href="${CONTACT_LINK}">${CONTACT_LABEL}</a>.
    </footer>
  </article>
</body>
</html>
